com.ibasco.agql.core.util

Interface Options

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Iterable<Map.Entry<Option<?>,Object>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractOptions, ConnectOptions, FailsafeOptions, GeneralOptions, HttpOptions, MasterServerOptions, SourceQueryOptions, SourceRconOptions

    public interface Options
extends Cloneable, Iterable<Map.Entry<Option<?>,Object>>
    A container for configuration Option instances. Implementation of this must be thread-safe.
    Author:
    Rafael Luis Ibasco

      • put

        <X> void put(Option<X> option,
             X value,
             boolean locked)

        Add option value to this container with the additional option to lockout the value

        Type Parameters:
        X - The captured type of the Option
        Parameters:
        option - The Option key to be used as lookup
        value - The value to be added
        locked - Set to true if we should lockout this value. Future invocations of put(Option, Object) will result in failure for this configuration Option
